title: FANTASTIC FOUR VISIONARIES JOHN BYRNE 0-8 and GEORGE PEREZ 1-2
description:
This torrent contains:
Fantastic Four Visionaries - John Byrne - Volume 1 to Volume 8 and Volume 0
Fantastic Four Visionaries - George Perez - Volume 1 and Volume 2

11 collected editions in all, most scanned by the amazing Bchry-DCP. All credit belongs to him. Thanks to SleepMan for posting Volume 7 on Thursday, which I'd been missing.

Now if we can just collect FF Visionaries Walt Simonson, we'll be good!  :-)
